        <updateDate>2017-10-23T15:21:17Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>No Taxpayer Revenue Used to Monetize the Presidency Act of 2017 or the No TRUMP Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits direct payments from the Treasury or reimbursements for any amounts expended in a hotel or other establishment providing daily-rate accommodation that is owned or operated by the President or a relative of the President.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
